   Le sac du Berger | The leather workshop
   Since 1980, at the beginning alone at his workbench, Jean-Pierre
   Romiguier, manager and founder, worked to "sew" the deep link that
   embraces and brings past and modernity, ethics and economy, distant
   memory and infinite future: from this quest arose Le Sac du Berger by
   itself.
   Sac, berger, artisanat, cuir, atelier, traditionnel, fabrication,
   entreprise, patrimoine, vivant, française, Layrolle, Aveyron, Hérault,
   Midi-Pyrénées, France, maroquinerie, sellerie, confection, vêtements,
